        public static <V extends Vertex,E extends Edge<V>> Embedding<V,E> emedGraph(Graph<V,E> graph,
                                                                            V s,
                                                                            V t)
                                                                     throws CannotBeAppliedException
        Calculates a planar embedding of a graph based on the work of Chiba, Nishizeki, Abe and Ozava A linear algorithm for embedding planar graphs using PQ-trees, Journal of Computer and System Sciences 30, 1985
        Type Parameters:
        V - The vertex type
        E - The edge type
        Parameters:
        graph - Graph whose embedding should be found
        s - The first vertex of the ST-numbering
        t - The last vertex of the ST-numbering
        Returns:
        Planar embedding if it exists
        Throws:
        CannotBeAppliedException - if the graph is not planar
